* [[Adrian Caesar|Caesar, Adrian]]: ''The White: Last Days in the Antarctic Journeys of Scott and Mawson 1911–1913'' Pan MacMillan, Sydney, 1999, {{ISBN|978-0-330-36157-6}}
* {{cite book
  | last = Huxley
  | first = Elspeth
